data.description: Completely remodeled end unit! Walk into an open living area with stone fireplace and prewired wall for mounted TV. Kitchen has maple cabinets, newer granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances! Laundry room is equipped with washer and dryer and the mechanical room includes furnace and a newer installed hot water heater (2019). Upstairs bedrooms include the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and an adjoining bathroom. The guest bedroom also has a walk-in closet. This townhome includes a covered carport with a locked storage closet.     Centrally located with close proximity to Palmer Park, schools. shopping, and dining.
